==English==

===Noun===
'''[[plume]] [[grass]]'''
# {{botany}} A kind of [[grass]] (''Erianthus saccharoides'') with the [[spikelet]]s arranged in great [[silky]] plumes, growing in [[swamp]]s in the Southern United States.
# {{botany}} The still finer ''Erianthus Ravennae'' from the [[Mediterranean]] region. The name is sometimes extended to the whole genus.

